comments: Duren (DET) grasps and then quickly releases Allen's (CLE) jersey and marginal contact occurs during the shot attempt at the basket.
Duren (DET) and Allen (CLE) pursue the loose ball and marginal arm contact occurs as Allen secures the rebound.
Ivey (DET) reaches for the ball and marginal contact occurs with Allen's (CLE) left arm after he secures the rebound.
Duren (DET) establishes himself in Strus' (CLE) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Duren (DET) establishes himself in Okoro's (CLE) path as he firms up on his right foot and does not deliver illegal contact during the screen.
DET commits a 24 second shot-clock violation.
Allen (CLE) brings his hands toward Ivey (DET) and marginal contact occurs as Allen releases away to roll.
Ivey (DET) moves into Mitchell's (CLE) body and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.

Ivey (DET) reaches for the ball and he initiates illegal contact with Mitchell's (CLE) face. Burks (DET) swipes down and makes contact with the ball following the contact with Mitchell's face. The personal foul should have been assessed to Ivey.
LeVert (CLE) engages with Ivey (DET) off-ball and marginal contact occurs as LeVert releases away for a potential inbound pass.
Bogdanovic (DET) commits a take foul on Mitchell (CLE).
Mitchell (CLE) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
